{"lastModified":1772628647923,"uri":"c::8193426698::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60","yachtType":["Motor","Power Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia, Montenegro\n\nCharter AMBER ONE, Sunreef 70 POWER avaiable in Croatia and Monte Negro. This 70 Sunreef Power continues the legacy of Sunreef Yachts’ seaworthy motor yachts. The Sunreef 70 AMBER ONE is an all-around leisure yacht ideal for exclusive getaways and adventures. A striking 70-foot motor catamaran in a rich dark brown hue (with golden finish in sunset) commands attention with its powerful and robust design. Its sleek, streamlined silhouette suggests speed and agility, while the spacious layout features four double en suite cabins, offering luxurious comfort for guests. The well-appointed interiors blend modern elegance with functionality, providing an inviting atmosphere for relaxation. Expansive decks invite sunbathing and outdoor dining, making this catamaran an ideal choice for both adventure seekers and those looking to unwind in style. Its impressive presence on the water is sure to turn heads and create unforgettable experiences. The 70 Sunreef Power boasts a large bow terrace for lounging protected from sun and wind. The aft cockpit provides an alfresco dining space close to the water as well as a great spot to enjoy water sports with easy access to toys and PWCs.\n\nExperienced and Reliable Crew \nA crew of four (captain, chef, stewardess & deck-hand), all trained professionals with experience in their fields, will make you feel like you are on your own yacht and make sure you have privacy but still be catered to. Captain Boris expertly navigates the waters, ensuring your safety and enjoyment. Chef Gaga prepares the delicious meals tailord to your tastes using the fresh local ingredients. Stewardess Maria provides personalised, thoughtful service to make you feel at home while the deckhand keeps everything running smoothly, from docking to watertoys, Together, they create a seamless and relaxing experience, allowing you to simply unwind and enjoy every moment on board AMBER ONE. \n\n","blueprint":{"name":"AMBER ONE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c050980-da92-11ef-82ed-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c05f3e0-da92-11ef-82ed-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c064200-da92-11ef-84af-9f416608b899/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c05a5c0-da92-11ef-84af-9f416608b899/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c075370-da92-11ef-82ee-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c10f060-da92-11ef-b2ca-1f4cd8444a7a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c05a5c0-da92-11ef-82ee-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c07c8a0-da92-11ef-82ee-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c0ad5e0-da92-11ef-932a-fd3a354ffa86/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c10f060-da92-11ef-9b33-5ba5459d80e9/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c1201d0-da92-11ef-b2ca-1f4cd8444a7a/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c069020-da92-11ef-82ee-49662a300e6b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c03a9f0-da92-11ef-ae72-07d666c9e810/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::77940a05-486c-11ee-a45f-fdfff6163a60::assets::7c04e270-da92-11ef-84af-9f416608b899/{imageVarian